{
  "video_id": "5ux-UdMGFlA",
  "title": "Trump to meet Kim, World Cup kicks off",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 2739.0,
      "end_time": 4279.0,
      "text": "Hello and welcome to \"The Week Ahead\""
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4280.0,
      "end_time": 5970.0,
      "text": "from the Financial Times in London."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5970.0,
      "end_time": 8809.0,
      "text": "Here are some of the big stories we'll be watching this week."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8810.0,
      "end_time": 10970.0,
      "text": "Historic talks between the US and North Korea"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10970.0,
      "end_time": 13370.0,
      "text": "will take place when Donald Trump and Kim Jong Un"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13370.0,
      "end_time": 15490.0,
      "text": "meet in Singapore."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15500.0,
      "end_time": 17420.0,
      "text": "The Federal Reserve is expected to raise interest rates"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17420.0,
      "end_time": 18800.0,
      "text": "in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 18800.0,
      "end_time": 21140.0,
      "text": "The owner of the Zara fashion brand, Inditex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21140.0,
      "end_time": 22730.0,
      "text": "reports results."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22730.0,
      "end_time": 24890.0,
      "text": "And the football World Cup kicks off in Russia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24890.0,
      "end_time": 26720.0,
      "text": "but will FIFA vote for an underdog"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26720.0,
      "end_time": 29330.0,
      "text": "to host the 2026 tournament?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 29330.0,
      "end_time": 32509.0,
      "text": "Now, just a year ago, Kim Jong Un was a pariah."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 32509.0,
      "end_time": 35120.0,
      "text": "North Korea had conducted several missile tests"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 35120.0,
      "end_time": 37309.0,
      "text": "and US President Donald Trump threatened"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 37310.0,
      "end_time": 39770.0,
      "text": "to respond with fire and fury."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 39770.0,
      "end_time": 41810.0,
      "text": "Until March, the North Korean dictator"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 41810.0,
      "end_time": 44540.0,
      "text": "had never even been abroad on a state visit."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 44540.0,
      "end_time": 47600.0,
      "text": "But this year, things have switched to a more diplomatic"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 47600.0,
      "end_time": 49250.0,
      "text": "track, and on Tuesday he's due to meet Donald"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 49250.0,
      "end_time": 51620.0,
      "text": "Trump in a historic summit."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 51620.0,
      "end_time": 53449.0,
      "text": "Mr Trump wants to sign an agreement"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 53450.0,
      "end_time": 56150.0,
      "text": "to denuclearize North Korea and set a new path"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 56150.0,
      "end_time": 58700.0,
      "text": "for the reclusive regime."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 58700.0,
      "end_time": 60830.0,
      "text": "But what is the US likely to get out of this week's meeting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 60830.0,
      "end_time": 64220.0,
      "text": "Here's our chief foreign affairs commentator, Gideon Rachman."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 64220.0,
      "end_time": 67910.0,
      "text": "These are two very unusual and unpredictable leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 67910.0,
      "end_time": 69979.0,
      "text": "If you had two kind of normal leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 69980.0,
      "end_time": 72830.0,
      "text": "it would be quite easy, I think, to sketch out"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 72830.0,
      "end_time": 75660.0,
      "text": "the possible outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 75660.0,
      "end_time": 78710.0,
      "text": "It would be very hard to imagine that they would immediately"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 78710.0,
      "end_time": 82580.0,
      "text": "solve the problem or come up with a breakthrough."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 82580.0,
      "end_time": 84289.0,
      "text": "With these leaders, it's possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 84290.0,
      "end_time": 86534.0,
      "text": "that they will stray off script quite sharply"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 86534.0,
      "end_time": 88575.0,
      "text": "and perhaps come up with something with surprises"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 88575.0,
      "end_time": 89270.0,
      "text": "us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 89270.0,
      "end_time": 91000.0,
      "text": "But there's also a downside risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 91000.0,
      "end_time": 92790.0,
      "text": "And if the two men don't hit it off"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 92790.0,
      "end_time": 95810.0,
      "text": "or if they have very different expectations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 95810.0,
      "end_time": 98180.0,
      "text": "you could actually see a summit that goes badly wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 98180.0,
      "end_time": 100340.0,
      "text": "and leads to a return or even perhaps"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 100340.0,
      "end_time": 105660.0,
      "text": "an increase in concerns about war that so dominated 2017."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 105660.0,
      "end_time": 107810.0,
      "text": "And now to the US, where the Federal Reserve's"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 107810.0,
      "end_time": 109700.0,
      "text": "monetary policy decision is the highlight"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 109700.0,
      "end_time": 112190.0,
      "text": "of a busy economic calendar this week."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 112190.0,
      "end_time": 115390.0,
      "text": "We'll get updates on inflation, manufacturing, and consumer"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 115400.0,
      "end_time": 117847.0,
      "text": "sentiment in Thursday's retail sales report."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 117847.0,
      "end_time": 119929.0,
      "text": "The interest rate decision, which is on Wednesday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 119930.0,
      "end_time": 122300.0,
      "text": "will be presented alongside updates to the Fed's"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 122300.0,
      "end_time": 124289.0,
      "text": "economic and interest rate projections."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 124289.0,
      "end_time": 126800.0,
      "text": "That will be followed by a press conference"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 126800.0,
      "end_time": 128210.0,
      "text": "with fed chair Jay Powell."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 128210.00000000001,
      "end_time": 129800.00000000001,
      "text": "A rate rise is largely considered"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 129800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134660.0,
      "text": "a foregone conclusion, as our reporter Mamta Badkar explains."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 134660.0,
      "end_time": 136730.0,
      "text": "Markets are anticipating the second rate rise"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 136730.0,
      "end_time": 139880.0,
      "text": "of the year and the seventh since 2015 amid signs"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 139880.0,
      "end_time": 142170.0,
      "text": "of renewed strength in the US economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 142170.0,
      "end_time": 144200.0,
      "text": "and as the Fed is getting a bit more confident"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 144200.0,
      "end_time": 146790.0,
      "text": "about its inflation outlook."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 146800.0,
      "end_time": 148610.0,
      "text": "Now, the Fed said last month that inflation has moved closer"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 148610.0,
      "end_time": 152630.0,
      "text": "to its 2% target, but noted that this is a symmetrical target,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 152630.0,
      "end_time": 155960.0,
      "text": "suggesting that modest moves above or below 2%"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 155960.0,
      "end_time": 158150.0,
      "text": "will be acceptable to the Fed."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 158150.0,
      "end_time": 160970.0,
      "text": "Of note, of course, will be at the dot plot of interest rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 160970.0,
      "end_time": 163580.0,
      "text": "projections as markets try to determine"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 163580.0,
      "end_time": 167670.0,
      "text": "whether 2018 has three or four rate rises on the cards."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 167670.0,
      "end_time": 170510.0,
      "text": "Now to Spain, where Inditex, the owner of the Zara fashion"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 170510.0,
      "end_time": 173410.0,
      "text": "brand, is set to report its first quarter results."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 173410.0,
      "end_time": 175970.0,
      "text": "And all eyes will be on the long troublesome gross margin"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 175970.0,
      "end_time": 176660.0,
      "text": "figure."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 176660.0,
      "end_time": 179210.0,
      "text": "The world's largest clothes retailer by sales"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 179210.0,
      "end_time": 181490.0,
      "text": "has for years seen slipping margins."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 181490.0,
      "end_time": 183230.0,
      "text": "This has sparked investor concerns"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 183230.0,
      "end_time": 186259.0,
      "text": "about the effects of competition from online only rivals."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 186259.0,
      "end_time": 188299.0,
      "text": "And in March, the company said that gross margins"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 188300.0,
      "end_time": 193760.0,
      "text": "had dropped from 57% in 2016 to 56.3% in 2017."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 193760.0,
      "end_time": 196190.0,
      "text": "That was the lowest for a decade and worse"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 196200.0,
      "end_time": 197570.0,
      "text": "than analysts' expectations."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 197570.0,
      "end_time": 200239.0,
      "text": "But many analysts are saying that while gross margins may"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 200240.0,
      "end_time": 201800.0,
      "text": "be down in the first quarter, there"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 201800.0,
      "end_time": 203960.0,
      "text": "could be signs of stabilisation, which"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 203960.0,
      "end_time": 205530.0,
      "text": "would reassure the markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 205530.0,
      "end_time": 208000.0,
      "text": "Inditex has long denied that online sales will lead them"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 208000.0,
      "end_time": 209240.0,
      "text": "to lower margins."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 209240.0,
      "end_time": 212000.0,
      "text": "Earlier this year, it blamed the strong euro, as well as"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 212000.0,
      "end_time": 214290.0,
      "text": "unseasonal weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 214290.0,
      "end_time": 216290.0,
      "text": "And finally, to Russia, where the football World"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 216290.0,
      "end_time": 218150.0,
      "text": "Cup kicks off on Thursday."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 218150.0,
      "end_time": 221420.0,
      "text": "The host take on Saudi Arabia in the opening match in Moscow."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 221420.0,
      "end_time": 223549.0,
      "text": "But just before the big kickoff, more than 200"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 223550.0,
      "end_time": 225200.0,
      "text": "of FIFA's member nations will meet"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 225200.0,
      "end_time": 227989.0,
      "text": "to vote on the host for the 2026 World Cup."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 227990.0,
      "end_time": 230240.0,
      "text": "And it's a race between a powerhouse joint bid"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 230240.0,
      "end_time": 232550.0,
      "text": "by the United States, Canada, and Mexico"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 232550.0,
      "end_time": 234800.0,
      "text": "and an underdog bid by Morocco."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 234800.0,
      "end_time": 236300.0,
      "text": "Much to the surprise of many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 236300.0,
      "end_time": 238261.0,
      "text": "in the world of football, Morocco could win it."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 238261.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "This would be a shock because the North American"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 243769.0,
      "text": "bid is offering a projected record $11 billion of profits"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 243770.0,
      "end_time": 244680.0,
      "text": "to FIFA."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 244680.0,
      "end_time": 246680.0,
      "text": "And FIFA's own inspection task force"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 246680.0,
      "end_time": 249580.0,
      "text": "scored the North American bid very highly on technical merits"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 249580.0,
      "end_time": 251240.0,
      "text": "and it said there were risks to hosting"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 251240.0,
      "end_time": 252600.0,
      "text": "the tournament in Morocco."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 252600.0,
      "end_time": 255859.0,
      "text": "So what would it mean if Morocco pulls off a surprise victory?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 255860.0,
      "end_time": 258110.0,
      "text": "Here's our leisure correspondent, Murad Ahmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 258110.0,
      "end_time": 260000.0,
      "text": "It seemed to me, at least, by reading"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 260000.0,
      "end_time": 263150.0,
      "text": "that report that FIFA's inspectors were saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 263150.0,
      "end_time": 265400.0,
      "text": "don't hold the World Cup in Morocco, at least"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 265400.0,
      "end_time": 268489.0,
      "text": "in comparison to the North American bid."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 268490.0,
      "end_time": 271250.0,
      "text": "So what would it say if Morocco still won?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 271250.0,
      "end_time": 274400.0,
      "text": "It would tell you that the political horse"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 274400.0,
      "end_time": 278690.0,
      "text": "trading of the past that has mired old World Cup votes"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 278690.0,
      "end_time": 281630.0,
      "text": "has not disappeared, regardless of all the reforms"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 281630.0,
      "end_time": 283969.0,
      "text": "that FIFA have put in place."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 283970.0,
      "end_time": 286700.0,
      "text": "And weirdly enough, a counterpoint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 286700.0,
      "end_time": 289390.0,
      "text": "that money isn't everything, that"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 289400.0,
      "end_time": 292880.0,
      "text": "in the end, the global image that you set out"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 292880.0,
      "end_time": 295969.0,
      "text": "has a big part to play when it comes"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 295970.0,
      "end_time": 299730.0,
      "text": "to voting on these essentially popularity contests."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 299730.0,
      "end_time": 302230.0,
      "text": "And that's what the week ahead looks like from the Financial"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 302230.0,
      "end_time": 303170.0,
      "text": "Times in London."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 303170.0,
      "end_time": 305280.0,
      "text": "See you again next time."
    }
  ]
}